<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa ini...</font>

46
00:03:39,170 --> 00:03:41,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia melakukan hal sia-sia?</font>

47
00:03:41,770 --> 00:03:43,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu pergi mencari tablet?</font>

48
00:03:43,010 --> 00:03:45,540
